" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249e00156008e25545beb091bcd1b71e3763f20b","tid":2129233,"uid":306738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:42:45.000Z","msg":"人之前在北歐<br />\n三月到五月啲餐廳大部分唔開<br />\n開既都係連鎖快餐Pizza之類<br />\n可以咁做因為政府完全補貼<br />\n本地人真係唔太出街<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">識得大劣人係咁house party</span></strong><br />\n不過見到佢地想番支那<br />\nBook機票係咁被cancel好心涼"},{"pid":"a7614c45d93003ddddbc4060c1c5909a0dd6d1b1","tid":2129233,"uid":1430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:43:31.000Z","msg":"人地禁堂食得黎都lockdown 強制wfh<br />\n咁咪無人需要擔心返工無地方食飯囉"},{"pid":"c8eed9d2983854ab339f834f1ddaa7f60f9bb042","tid":2129233,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:43:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">Youtube戰線要人！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個youtube channel<strong><span class=\"purple\"><ins>專呃廢老，心腸歹毒</ins></span></strong>！<br />\n見佢又用蝗語又用殘體等人以為佢係藍絲自己友？<br />\n點知原來係個<strong><ins><span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">偽藍真黃嘅文宣長輩台</span></span></ins></strong>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/u6jvUrxfY2Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fu6jvUrxfY2Y&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD9mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=4cba28fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/u6jvUrxfY2Y</a><br />\n睇下呢段片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />扮晒做廢老鍾意睇嘅恥笑美國不行了，點知睇睇下都不忘插幾下鄭月娥推禁堂食令離地，又話政府唔封關免檢疫先搞到第三波爆發，好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得記得，千祈千祈要懲罰呢個channel，唔好畀like，都唔好幫屋企人偷偷訂閱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5a87194b4b9be7cceb647698b0db661edc8d9e","tid":2129233,"uid":279457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:44:24.000Z","msg":"屌 on9正苦，香港唔同外國<br />\n<br />\n外國地方大，揸車去森林裡面食都得，打埋飛機都仲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港街口與街口之間近，每個人買完外賣<br />\n<br />\n隨便搵個地方食都難，仲要係高度密集地方一齊開餐，唔受感染之奇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜嫁仲要禁埋堂食，咁等於同之前on9政策「室內無限制，室外限制50人」有咩分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信會加快人傳人速度，同埋派支那醫生黎香港更進一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f947fafeb9ebb55587951c81eac3899d0f9bb776","tid":2129233,"uid":154486,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"fbc0a93420d45dd0fb1936724e67922267d1ba35","tid":2129233,"uid":130406,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"06728bc290b78055856c37267ca147dec555f64f","tid":2129233,"uid":1544,"like":309,"dislike":2,"score":307,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T12:41:34.000Z","msg":"人地本身都自己煮開 <br />\n就算買外賣都大把地方食"},"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T12:47:26.000Z","msg":"講緊返工食飯 唔通中午返屋企煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺外國唔係office/司機/固定地點 返工嗰堆<br />\n戶外工作嘅 例如地盤工人<br />\n外國佢地點解決"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:44:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">果陣停左工</span></strong>"},{"pid":"4cf5d6eb8eb017d4147d235864f4474f7d780e26","tid":2129233,"uid":362900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:44:51.000Z","msg":"係車入面食又得<br />\n<br />\n公司又大撚把地方食"},{"pid":"8d7f3d1afc9efebb15efc4321229e1b26353ab1d","tid":2129233,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:45:00.000Z","msg":"香港長凳都唔多個"},{"pid":"13ccd7ad1ff13bcba31718a697c2cfdcd2d4c8d9","tid":