 />\n又抄啲唔抄啲<br />\n好好地一個香港搞到一街乞衣咁<br />\n踎係地食 係後欄食 係廁所食<br />\n真係好撚心酸"},{"pid":"7a53cd3fa4b47e67dc9ab62ddf8e40c77ed8d8a1","tid":2129233,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:55:45.000Z","msg":"我記得人地係連地盤都停埋工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba862c5da952a4a0eae58e472af7ab001be69378","tid":2129233,"uid":168104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:59:17.000Z","msg":"坐響部車入面食"},{"pid":"5dac2acd48da3eec7067aa03d6be9b63764a7dbe","tid":2129233,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"291267310702d9e01737550216fef259b8913595","tid":2129233,"uid":211466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"26c2c142ceee0412dd8fc15200213b03ea662a96","tid":2129233,"uid":261913,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"59c4bd10d7124f37128601d523b24c36a27780cb","tid":2129233,"uid":211466,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:05:44.000Z","msg":"真, D 鬼都唔食lunch ge"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:11:16.000Z","msg":"食<br />\n但係食包 仲要係凍包<br />\n所以係邊食都無所謂 揸住車食都得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:12:51.000Z","msg":"好似D 日本仔都係噤上下, 一路搭新幹線, 一路食個飯團, 仲要係就咁用保鮮紙包住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:02:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/171909_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F171909_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e27a267b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0323e5c7369c871ce19e96ebaf2192bc3e62a810","tid":2129233,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:06:09.000Z","msg":"因為地產商係贏家"},{"pid":"e3acebdd10c04bcb672322a712f1bde1c2b0a203","tid":2129233,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"